\b Nocturnal Toolkit Project Notes\b0\par
\par
\b Current Identity\b0\par
TN Toolkit is now a Tauri 2 + Rust + React project for macOS, Windows, and Android.\par
Official URL: https://toolkit.team-nocturnal.com\par
Forum thread: https://forums.wbodytech.com/%E2%9A%A1-nocturnal-toolkit-by-team-nocturnal.t239/\par
\par
\b Current Positioning\b0\par
- Desktop build is the main control center for ADB, Fastboot, app installs, file browsing, backups, maintenance, TV tools, Quest tools, and ROM workflows.\par
- Android build is intentionally mobile-first and local-device-first instead of mirroring the desktop UI exactly.\par
- Desktop and Android should stay separated where platform-specific UX makes more sense.\par
\par
\b Release State\b0\par
- Current version: 2.0.0-beta.6\par
- macOS build output: TN Toolkit.app and TN Toolkit_2.0.0-beta.6_aarch64.dmg\par
- Android APK/AAB packaging is working, but macOS signing and notarization are still pending.\par
\par
