\b UI / Product Notes\b0\par
- Desktop sidebar now uses Getting Started, Apps, Devices, Media, Power Tools, Pro Tools, and Help.\par
- File Browser is restored as its own direct panel.\par
- Backup & Restore, Maintenance, Tweaks, Quest Tools, and ROM Tools were reorganized for cleaner flow.\par
- Pro Tools now contains deeper ADB and advanced functionality.\par
- Media section is being cleaned up into clearer device/media groupings.\par
