\par
\b Build / Cleanup Notes\b0\par
- Generated build output can get very large. Safe cleanup targets include:\par
  src-tauri/target\par
  dist\par
  src-tauri/gen/android/app/build\par
  src-tauri/gen/android/build\par
- These folders can be deleted anytime before rebuilding.\par
\par
\b General Direction\b0\par
Keep TN Toolkit feeling like a polished power-user utility, not a loose collection of random panels. Prefer grouping by actual workflow and avoid duplicate tools in multiple places.\par
